{"tid":2053400,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拆輔警總監僭建屋 地政拖足兩年半  村民斥執法雙重標準","createTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T14:48:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3832413d074a485f803a028f9fcdd243f9268ce4","tid":2053400,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200606/OPFE6QSCIF7I7HVKCGJYU7FHGA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200606%2FOPFE6QSCIF7I7HVKCGJYU7FHGA%2F&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx4ICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=13ef7745\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200606%2FOPFE6QSCIF7I7HVKCGJYU7FHGA%2F&h=e5935fef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200606/OPFE6QSCIF7I7HVKCGJYU7FHGA/</a><br />\n<br />\n拆輔警總監僭建屋 地政拖足兩年半 <br />\n村民斥執法雙重標準<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警務處助理處長陶輝早前被揭僭建及霸佔官地，有村民早於2014年向地政署舉報卻遲遲不獲處理。本報跟進發現，輔助警察隊總監楊祖賜的西貢北港新村村屋，原來亦曾被投訴僭建及霸官地；地政總署在2017年覆信確認收到投訴人舉報，惟同樣不作跟進。相反，該署處理同村其他類似個案時，卻「揸正嚟做」飭令村民在一至數月限期內糾正，執法力度明顯有別。<br />\n<br />\n記者：調查組<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/EQ4DN2CHWA44F4TCOP3TKKCNB4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FEQ4DN2CHWA44F4TCOP3TKKCNB4.gif&h=955641bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有市民早於2017年向地政署舉報，更標示楊祖賜霸佔官地範圍（上圖），地政署同年回信確認指控（下圖）。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n楊祖賜早於2011年購入北港新村單號屋，今年5月中被傳媒揭發涉僭。。。。。。。。。。求的地方；地政總署在5月下旬確認上址佔用政府土地，已飭令佔用人於限期前停止佔用。<br />\n<br />\n有知情人士向本報提供電郵紀錄，顯示有巿民早於2017年10月已向地政署舉報事件，投訴屋主圍封官地作私人花園及泊車。。。。。。。。。。。 on Government land），將調查及跟進，並附上個案編號。不過，違規情況拖延至今未被糾正，前後足足兩年半。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士又透露，除楊祖賜的單號屋外，去年同村亦有其他村屋被舉。。。。。。。。。。。地政總署）搵人嚟拆，拆完再向屋主收番費用。」違規情況最終在兩至三個月內被糾正，該署事後更派員到場檢視。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n議員質疑包庇警高層<br />\n<br />\n至於陶輝的碧水新村牌照屋早前被揭發僭建及霸官地，區議員及村民亦。。。。。。。。。。。已被移除，天台屋外圍的冷氣機也被拆走，正準備進行拆卸工程。<br />\n<br />\n記者上月1日至今多次以電郵及電話查詢地政總署，要求提供涉事北港。。。。。。。。。。。該署拒絕回覆。記者已按《公開資料守則》，向地政總署公開資料主任索取資料。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員林卓廷質疑地政總署執法雙重標準，涉嫌包庇警隊。。。。。。。。。。。。隊高層，現階段需更多證據支持。林又批評該署拒答傳媒查詢，「只會顯示佢哋心虛」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FZ4OUNMCNIYRZR24LY36PGIJOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFZ4OUNMCNIYRZR24LY36PGIJOY.jpg&h=acbf4456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n楊祖賜"},{"pid":"e5d38ebf98c8a637a339d3bf3f675060b43ceec9","tid":2053400,"uid":3135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:18:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"980b155f91447df4d28441e5b597927f7ed42c49","tid":2053400,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:09:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a28c1dc969756d9d3daac7de88eee625576d637b","tid":2053400,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761e6c5e16001428d1a3a7d90f98302dfc76d2d6","tid":2053400,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:16:21.000Z","msg":"警隊由上至下都犯晒法"},{"pid":"a7af213c79e68e5be820228082b5bd1b1fe25ce1","tid":2053400,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"冇雙重標準<br />\n標準咪就係睇你係唔係阿sir<br />\n你係sir一樣可以犯法冇後果<br />\n可惜你唔係阿sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2784518642038b07f8ca93e29aceb26ced922d60","tid":2053400,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"推"}]}